<HEADLINE>
<P>
STORCH BLACKBALLED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I have had the honored privilege of knowing Judge Lawrence Storch for many 
years and have participated in thoughtful discussions with him. He is a person 
of quality, honor and admiration. 
</P>
<P>
 I have also known Dist. Atty. Michael D. Bradbury from the time he was a young 
