 * Sculpting workshops for children are being offered from 10 a.m. to noon and 
2 to 4 p.m. at Sculpture Spaces, 17911 Bushard St., Fountain Valley. $2. Call 
for reservations. (714) 964-6620. 
</P>
<P>
 * "The Stars of Tomorrow," a day of workshops and performances focusing on 
music and dance, is from 10:15 a.m. to 5 p.m. at Fashion Island Newport Beach. 
Free. (714) 556-2787, Ext. 888. 
</P>
<P>
 * "A Celebration of Visual Art," featuring more than 1,000 artworks by local 
children, and hands-on art workshops, opens at the Brea Mall, State College 
Boulevard and Imperial Highway, Brea. Hours today: 11 a.m. to 4 p.m. Free. 
Through May 1. (714) 990-2732. 
</P>
