 * The Blake Gallery, at 16062 Beach Blvd. in Huntington Beach, is holding a 
meet-the-artists day from 11 a.m to 5 p.m. and a student photography show on 
view through May 1. Free. (714) 841-7551. 
</P>
<P>
 * Children's vocal trio Sharon, Lois & Bram appears at 2:30 p.m. at the Orange 
County Performing Arts Center, 600 Town Center Drive, Costa Mesa. $4. (714) 
556-2787, Ext. 888, or (714) 740-2000 (TicketMaster). 
</P>
