 RAMS RALLY: If you're one of those worried about the Rams moving to Eastern 
pastures, the team's Booster Club would like to see you at Anaheim Stadium 
today. Club members are having a rally there from noon to 3 p.m. -- with Rams 
cheerleaders -- to show support for keeping the Rams in Anaheim. . . . Some of 
the Rams must want to stay too. Several players will attend and even sign 
autographs for free. Jerry Hicks and Mimi Ko and Martin Miller 
