</P>
<P>
 The 13th annual SchoolPower Laguna Beach Classic 10K is the largest 
fund-raiser for local schools.This year, $1 from each entry fee will go 
directly to the rebuilding of Thurston Middle School, which was burned in the 
October fire. 
</P>
<P>
 Runners will begin their trek at the Sawdust Festival Grounds, racing through 
downtown, along Coast Highway and through Laguna Canyon. 
</P>
