$15. 
</P>
<P>
 Participants may register today at the Sawdust Festival Grounds from 2 to 4 
p.m. Registration will also be conducted Sunday before the race at the Sawdust 
Festival Grounds, beginning at 6:30 a.m. The 5K begins at 7:45 a.m., the 10K at 
8:20 a.m. and the 1K at 9:15 a.m. LESLIE EARNEST 
