 Tustin 4, Saddleback 3 -- Julio Villalobos had two hits and two RBIs, 
including the game-winning single in the fourth inning, for Tustin (15-5, 7-1). 
</P>
<P>
 John Lauderdale had two doubles for Tillers. 
</P>
<P>
