<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY COLLEGE SOFTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Orange Empire conference softball games: 
</P>
<P>
 Cypress 3, Rancho Santiago 0 -- Freshman Jenny Lopez gave up six hits and 
walked two for Cypress (36-14, 12-5), which won its ninth consecutive 
conference game.Briana Yoshina tripled in Lopez and Kerry Moloney in the third 
and on a single by Jennifer Allchin who went three for three. Rancho Santiago 
is 23-16, 11-6. 
</P>
<P>
 Golden West 14, Irvine Valley 3 (5, mercy) -- Nikki Mimms had four hits, three 
RBIs and three runs scored for Golden West (10-22, 5-12). 
