<TEXT>
<P>
 Show organizers -- Due to erroneous information provided by the Armand Hammer 
Museum of Art and Cultural Center, the March 31 Calendar review of the 
exhibition "Mexico Through Foreign Eyes: 1850-1990" incorrectly identified the 
show's organizers. Curators Carole Naggar and Fred Ritchin hired Pilar Perez 
and Associates to assist in administration and touring of the exhibition. 
</P>
</TEXT>
