<TEXT>
<P>
 Streisand's tour -- In Friday's Calendar story about Barbra Streisand's tour, 
the information at the end of the story misidentified one of the local 
organizations selling tickets to her sold-out shows at the Anaheim Pond. The 
organization is the Natural Resources Defense Council. 
</P>
