<HEADLINE>
<P>
1994 VENTURA COUNTY SCIENCE FAIR WINNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Public and private school students from across the county submitted 700 
entries to the 1994 Ventura County Science Fair held this week. A team of 80 
local scientists, teachers and other professionals spent hours evaluating the 
projects to come up with the following list of winners: 
</P>
<P>
 SIXTH GRADE 
</P>
<P>
 SUBJECT: Botany 1ST PLACE: Megan Gorcey -- Driffill 2ND PLACE: Richard Reyes 
-- Chaparral Middle 3RD PLACE: David Choi -- Pinecrest, Thousand Oaks 
</P>
<P>
 SUBJECT: Chemistry/Biochemistry 1ST PLACE: Michael Oliver -- Ocean View Jr. 
High 2ND PLACE: Jean Dust -- Rose Avenue 3RD PLACE: Erin Jones -- Las Colinas 
Intermediate 
</P>
<P>
